; Coverage test for post.cc lines 313-318
; Tests display_account with virtual postings.
; Unbalanced virtual postings get () wrapping, balanced virtual get [].

2024/03/01 Test
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash      $-10.00
    (Budget:Food)     $5.00
    [Budget:Alloc]    $3.00
    [Budget:Rest]    $-3.00

test reg --format "%(display_account)\n"
Expenses:Food
Assets:Cash
(Budget:Food)
[Budget:Alloc]
[Budget:Rest]
end test
